headline: What Catalysts Are Quietly Rewriting The Story For i3 Verticals (IIIV)
summary: i3 Verticals just went through a fresh valuation check, and while the model fair value estimate holds steady at US$34.17, the inputs behind that number tell a more nuanced story. With revenue growth assumptions largely intact and only a small tweak to the discount rate, most of the change in the price target narrative comes back to when certain projects are expected to show up in reported numbers, not a wholesale rethink of the business. Stay tuned to see how you can keep on top of these...
